Privacy Policy
This APP respects and protects the privacy of all users who use the service. To provide you with more accurate and
                    personalized service, the APP will be in accordance with the provisions of this Privacy Policy to use and disclose your
                    personal information. But the APP will deal with this information with a high degree of diligence and prudence.
Except as otherwise provided in this Privacy Policy, this APP will not disclose or provide such information to third
                    parties without your prior permission. This APP will update this Privacy Policy from time to time. By agreeing to the
                    APP Agreement, you are deemed to have agreed to the entire contents of this Privacy Policy.This Privacy Policy is an
                    integral part of the APP Service Use Agreement.
Everyone has a different focus on privacy, and our goal is to specify exactly what information we collect so that you
                    can choose the way you use it.
1）
Personal registration information
When you register your account, you will be asked for personal registration information. Personal data will only be
                    transferred to your personal authorization. In addition, we only collect the data we need to maintain our company to
                    provide you with the service.
2）
Get account verification information
Personal data will only be transferred to your personal authorization to maintain our company to provide services for
                    you;
3）
Read the phone status and identity
We need to read your identity and phone status, we we will not collect or store the requested data, only through the
                    device identification, in order to adapt to our multi-language, better for you to provide services;
4）
Turn on microphone recording and voice
We need access to your device's microphone. We do not collect or store the requested data and can only be accessed
                    through the camera or receiver.
5）
Request the input method service
We need to request input method services, in order to according to different countries, regional switching language;
6）
Allow the program to discover and connect the device
Request the mobile device to allow the device to discover and identify, in order to achieve the mobile side to achieve
                    remote operation;
7）
Alarm push service is triggered after the vibration and notification
We need to request the alarm within the APP to provide a reminder of the service in order to timely feedback to inform
                    the user;
8）
Get your location: approximate location (based on network),precise location (based on GPS and network)
We need to request by calling GPS to analyze the mobile device location with the network;
9）
control the positioning update
We need to request a location update on a mobile device that is moving over the network;
10）
network communication
1．View the network connection
Displays the current network status of the mobile device：for example, the 4G network
2．Get Wi-Fi hotspot information
Displays information of the connected WLAN：for example, name；
3．View the WLAN connection；
4．Change the network connection status；
5．connecting to a WLAN network and disconnecting;
6．Full network access;
7．Obtain the network status and whether the network connection is valid;
11）
mobile web information
When you use APP web service or visit APP platform web pages, APP automatically receives and records your information,
                    including but not limited to your mobile web information, IP address, Wi-Fi access point, operating system version,
                    software version, the language used, the date and time of the visit, the characteristics of the hardware and software,
                    and the web page records you need;
12）
Application information
1．Retrieve the running application；
2．Powered up
