18）
Push notification
If you want to show our push notifications on mobile devices, you must grant us permission even if your application is
                    not open on your phone. The first time you start the application, we will ask for your permission. The application will
                    use this so-called push notification only if you explicitly agree. You can disable push notifications at any time in
